ratings.comment: Terrible!!!!!! His organization is probably the worst I have experienced in college, and all his assignments are unclear what you are supposed to do. The group project is the biggest waste of time as you don't learn anything in it, you are just trying to get it done. I spent way too many hours on this class for it only being 3 credits.

Professor Park did what he could for this corona semester. The online format definitely made it difficult but was a truly caring and inspirational man. He has a lot of knowledge, wisdom, and world travels that he likes to share with the class. He grades very easily and is more focused on what you can take away from the class. Little guidance howeve
